Folders structure:

/make-game-web 
  ├── res/
       ├── DARKSHAPE
       ├── SHAPE
       └──... (resources files)
  ├──src/
       ├── wrapper.c  
       ├── game.c
       ├── game.h
       └── ...
  ├── demo.js
  ├── game.html
  ├── Makefile
  └── README


These are some instructions to compile and run the game:
    1. Open the folder make-game-web with integrated terminal 
    2. "make all" to compile
    3. "make serve" to be able to access the game at http://localhost:8001/game.html
    After "make all" the folder structure should look like this
To compile the game, you need to have Emscripten installed on your machine. You can follow the instructions below to set it up:
    1. "git clone https://github.com/emscripten-core/emsdk.git"
    2. "cd emsdk"
    3. "./emsdk install latest"
    4. "./emsdk activate latest"
    5. "source ./emsdk_env.sh"

/make-game-web 
